description:
Bummed you couldn't attend the first live Unqualified show with Whitney Cummings? Well now you can get in on the fun! Join Anna, Sim and Whitney at the Nerdmelt Showroom in LA for a candid convo about Whitney's sexual past, bridal parties, and of course, some dealbreakers!  Anna also calls up on stage a very popular surprise guest. Don’t miss part two tomorrow when we take a live call and give one lucky audience member some unqualified relationship advice!

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
